WEBVTT

01:39.289 --> 01:43.729
[Road to Success]

01:44.789 --> 01:47.890
[Episode 9]

01:52.070 --> 01:53.130
Oh, it's really...

01:54.310 --> 01:55.590
Stop with this sarcastic tone,

01:55.590 --> 01:57.120
or I'll kick you out of here.

01:59.950 --> 02:01.350
Let me ask you a question.

02:03.120 --> 02:05.180
Did you sleep at her place last night?

02:07.640 --> 02:09.370
Did you not change your clothes

02:09.590 --> 02:12.190
or take a bath?
There's no bathtub at her place.

02:17.190 --> 02:18.920
Why are you giving me that look?

02:20.400 --> 02:22.260
Let's discuss an academic issue.

02:22.560 --> 02:24.950
How did she get so good?

02:24.970 --> 02:26.750
She's even better than a British doctor.

02:26.750 --> 02:28.079
She uses aromatherapy.

02:30.490 --> 02:31.600
Aromatherapy...

02:32.110 --> 02:32.940
Impressive.

02:33.400 --> 02:34.360
Speak your mind.

02:34.360 --> 02:35.310
What exactly are you up to?

02:35.310 --> 02:36.640
Why do have to be so dull?

02:37.560 --> 02:38.360
Alright.

02:38.840 --> 02:40.040
Let's talk business.

02:40.430 --> 02:42.000
How's your investigation on the likelihood

02:42.000 --> 02:43.600
of Lin Wanxing being Spade Q?

02:46.910 --> 02:48.910
They're 80% likely the same person.

02:49.000 --> 02:50.280
Eighty percent?

02:52.120 --> 02:53.710
That's basically a positive match.

02:53.710 --> 02:54.710
Not necessarily.

03:05.470 --> 03:06.840
Something's odd about you.

03:06.840 --> 03:08.910
You find her suspicious,

03:08.910 --> 03:10.680
yet you speak for her.

03:11.680 --> 03:12.910
Interesting.

03:16.750 --> 03:18.680
That's quite a nice watch of yours.

03:19.190 --> 03:20.420
But I think it's mine.

03:20.440 --> 03:21.710
I borrowed it

03:21.710 --> 03:23.590
along with the suit that day.

03:24.510 --> 03:27.140
You know I work at your sister's company.

03:27.190 --> 03:28.650
I must have a decent image.

03:28.710 --> 03:30.970
I can't let anyone look down on you,
can I?

03:31.360 --> 03:32.360
Speaking of which,

03:32.360 --> 03:33.579
look at this watch

03:33.670 --> 03:35.770
and my outfit today.

03:36.190 --> 03:38.000
How is it? I can make
a good brother-in-law for you, right?

03:38.000 --> 03:38.470
Come on,

03:38.470 --> 03:39.710
call me that now.

03:43.720 --> 03:45.190
I need to go for a morning run.

03:45.190 --> 03:46.030
You stay here

03:46.030 --> 03:46.910
and dream on it.

03:48.190 --> 03:49.870
What do you mean by "dream on it"?

03:49.870 --> 03:51.280
How very rude.

04:00.280 --> 04:00.890
Ms. Lin.

04:00.910 --> 04:01.590
-Coach.
-Ms. Lin.

04:01.590 --> 04:02.080
-Coach.
-Coach.

04:02.080 --> 04:02.840
Ms. Lin.

04:02.840 --> 04:03.400
Coach.

04:03.400 --> 04:03.840
Ms. Lin.

04:03.840 --> 04:05.190
-Coach.
-Hello, Ms. Lin.

04:05.190 --> 04:07.190
-Hello, Ms. Lin.
-Is everyone here?

04:08.310 --> 04:11.240
Today's training will be
a bit different from usual.

04:11.280 --> 04:12.590
Ms. Lin got you

04:12.590 --> 04:14.680
a professional-level class on tactics.

04:14.680 --> 04:16.269
You mean a lesson for pros?

04:16.950 --> 04:17.600
Yes.

04:17.829 --> 04:19.720
But forcing a lecture
about professional tactics

04:19.720 --> 04:21.070
on you right now is equal to

04:21.070 --> 04:23.470
having you learn to run
before you can walk.

04:23.510 --> 04:24.160
You'll stumble.

04:24.160 --> 04:24.870
No, we won't.

04:24.870 --> 04:25.950
We won't, Coach. We can make it.

04:25.950 --> 04:26.880
-Trust us.
-Yeah, Coach.

04:26.880 --> 04:28.240
-No way.
-We can make it.

04:29.070 --> 04:30.120
Nonetheless, next,

04:30.120 --> 04:31.980
I will give you a taste of success.

04:34.390 --> 04:35.870
What counts as a taste of success?

04:35.870 --> 04:37.270
It's easy to understand.

04:37.360 --> 04:38.310
It'll count as a success

04:38.310 --> 04:39.770
as long as you score a goal.

04:41.270 --> 04:41.800
Alright.

04:42.270 --> 04:43.600
Warm-up exercise, now.

04:44.570 --> 04:45.400
Assemble!

04:50.159 --> 04:52.360
Next, I'll instruct you on Tactic No. 1.

04:52.390 --> 04:53.450
Though it's basic,

04:53.560 --> 04:54.430
it's still beyond

04:54.430 --> 04:56.159
the capabilities of many of you.

04:56.159 --> 04:58.120
Coach, what is Tactic No. 1?

04:58.680 --> 05:00.000
The core of Tactic No. 1 lies in

05:00.000 --> 05:01.860
playing defense before offense.

05:02.120 --> 05:02.830
Fu Xinshu,

05:03.630 --> 05:05.560
tell us about the advantages

05:05.560 --> 05:07.090
of Lyujing, our rival team.

05:07.510 --> 05:09.090
Known as "the Hyenas,"

05:09.360 --> 05:11.950
among all youth training teams,
Lyujing is famous for being strong

05:11.950 --> 05:13.750
in offense, but weak in defense.

05:13.920 --> 05:14.720
That's right.

05:14.920 --> 05:17.260
So we'll fight their attacks
with stillness.

05:17.260 --> 05:18.830
Our defensive strategy this time

05:18.830 --> 05:20.720
is to constrict
the rival team's attacking front,

05:20.720 --> 05:22.600
while seeking a chance
to assume the offensive.

05:22.600 --> 05:24.100
Lyujing is best at rhythm,

05:24.120 --> 05:25.040
not stamina.

05:25.040 --> 05:26.360
You must stall and exhaust

05:26.360 --> 05:27.000
them.

05:30.040 --> 05:31.950
We'll resort to the 4-5-1 Formation
in the upcoming match.

05:31.950 --> 05:33.190
Defense before counterattacks.

05:33.190 --> 05:35.070
Fu Xinshu, Zhi Hui,
and Zheng Ren usually serve

05:35.070 --> 05:36.040
as midfield players.

05:36.040 --> 05:36.950
Chen Jianghe,

05:36.950 --> 05:38.159
I need you to retreat from the forward

05:38.159 --> 05:38.810
and play midfield.

05:38.810 --> 05:39.480
Got it.

05:39.480 --> 05:40.310
The 4-5-1 Formation

05:40.310 --> 05:42.080
requires all midfield players
to coordinate closely in defense,

05:42.080 --> 05:43.390
the forward to intersperse with agility,

05:43.390 --> 05:44.790
and the defenders
to hold the defense line tight.

05:44.790 --> 05:46.240
Qin Ao, since you'll be the only forward,

05:46.240 --> 05:47.020
the important task

05:47.020 --> 05:49.280
of assuming offense will be on you alone.

05:49.510 --> 05:50.480
Is that clear, boys?

05:50.480 --> 05:51.570
Wait.

05:51.590 --> 05:53.030
How come I don't get it?

05:54.390 --> 05:55.920
What don't you understand?

05:56.120 --> 05:58.000
The coach is looking out for you losers.

05:58.000 --> 05:59.659
Who are you calling "losers"?

06:00.040 --> 06:02.240
Don't you think
the coach wants to teach us something?

06:02.240 --> 06:03.360
He simply can't do that

06:03.360 --> 06:04.680
because there's no way
to get the message across.

06:04.680 --> 06:05.720
As for why that happens,

06:05.720 --> 06:07.240
try figuring it out yourselves.

06:07.240 --> 06:08.900
I'm off for warm-up exercise.

06:08.950 --> 06:10.000
-Qin Ao!
-Qin Ao.

06:10.630 --> 06:11.600
His harsh words are true, though.

06:11.600 --> 06:13.000
Ms. Lin fought really hard to get us

06:13.000 --> 06:13.800
this lesson, right?

06:13.800 --> 06:15.310
Yeah, it's very expensive.

06:15.310 --> 06:16.800
Please don't waste any time.

06:16.800 --> 06:17.720
That's right!

06:17.720 --> 06:18.600
To prove he's a clown,

06:18.600 --> 06:19.430
I must practice hard.

06:19.430 --> 06:20.190
-Exactly.
-Let's go!

06:20.190 --> 06:21.190
-Go.
-Let's go.

06:21.190 --> 06:22.250
Warm-up exercise.

06:35.250 --> 06:36.270
Watch the spacing.

06:36.270 --> 06:37.400
Keep the formation.

06:41.560 --> 06:43.350
Defenders, watch the distance
between each other.

06:43.350 --> 06:44.610
Spread out like a net!

06:46.380 --> 06:47.500
Zhi Hui, Zheng Ren,

06:47.530 --> 06:48.800
watch the spacing between you two.

06:48.800 --> 06:49.600
Eyes on the rope.

06:49.600 --> 06:50.360
Got it!

06:52.840 --> 06:56.100
Always mind your teammates
who have formed a defense line.

06:57.600 --> 07:00.330
With Wen Chengye,
a new player on the team,

07:00.730 --> 07:02.990
the morale seems to have truly improved.

07:03.160 --> 07:05.690
I feel like he'll give us
even more surprises.

07:07.600 --> 07:08.360
Nice shot!

07:09.040 --> 07:10.440
-This way. Here!
-Shoot!

07:15.720 --> 07:17.050
Did someone just score?

07:29.480 --> 07:30.920
For borrowing my cap once,

07:30.140 --> 07:31.350
[Receive Money by QR Code]

07:30.920 --> 07:31.510
you owe me 5 yuan.

07:31.510 --> 07:32.440
You're welcome.

07:44.159 --> 07:46.760
Seems like he's detained
by the teacher again.

07:46.950 --> 07:48.240
His skills...

07:48.240 --> 07:49.870
have never been up to par.

07:49.870 --> 07:51.000
Yeah.

07:51.000 --> 07:52.390
He's even bad at
copying others' moves, bro.

07:52.390 --> 07:53.800
Others go easy on him,

07:54.390 --> 07:55.830
but he never notices it.

07:58.070 --> 07:58.730
Hey, Mom.

07:59.000 --> 07:59.720
Xinshu,

08:00.120 --> 08:01.270
how have you been?

08:01.920 --> 08:04.600
Grandma told me
you started playing football again.

08:04.600 --> 08:05.830
I'm doing great, Mom.

08:05.830 --> 08:07.920
I just had a training session
with my pals this afternoon.

08:07.920 --> 08:09.980
-Today, we continued to...
-Xinshu,

08:10.270 --> 08:12.480
I'm having a minor surgery soon.

08:13.560 --> 08:16.010
Uncle Li is short of cash.

08:16.510 --> 08:18.240
So I wonder if I can borrow some from you.

08:18.240 --> 08:19.390
Mom, what surgery are you getting?

08:19.390 --> 08:20.160
And when?

08:20.160 --> 08:21.800
You... How about I come see you right now?

08:21.800 --> 08:23.160
-Just give me...
-No need.

08:23.160 --> 08:24.620
It's just a minor surgery.

08:24.680 --> 08:26.310
The exact time isn't confirmed yet.

08:26.310 --> 08:27.570
It's being scheduled.

08:28.680 --> 08:31.160
Mom, make sure
you take good care of yourself.

08:31.160 --> 08:33.090
I'll transfer money to you in a bit.

08:33.270 --> 08:33.960
Good.

08:35.270 --> 08:38.000
Send me the time and location
of your football game.

08:38.000 --> 08:39.400
I'll come watch you play.

08:40.240 --> 08:40.840
Great, Mom.

08:40.840 --> 08:41.789
I'll send you the info now.

08:41.789 --> 08:43.360
Then, later, I will...

08:56.190 --> 08:58.440
[You're transfering] [10,000 yuan]

09:02.100 --> 09:04.000
[You're transfering] [10,000 yuan]

09:06.590 --> 09:09.120
[You're transfering] [39,000 yuan]

09:12.370 --> 09:17.180
[Recipient Name: Guan Minjie]

09:20.270 --> 09:21.650
[Recipient Account Name: Guan Minjie]

09:25.030 --> 09:25.790
Mom,

09:25.790 --> 09:27.480
I've transferred money to you.

09:27.480 --> 09:29.750
I've also sent you
the location of the match.

09:29.750 --> 09:31.680
Don't forget to come watch me play.

09:32.960 --> 09:34.550
Fu, are you done there yet?

09:34.550 --> 09:35.630
Talking to your girlfriend or what?

09:35.630 --> 09:36.600
I'm coming!

09:37.790 --> 09:38.790
Hurry!

09:39.200 --> 09:41.150
Do you guys know what just happened?

09:41.150 --> 09:41.720
What?

09:41.720 --> 09:42.440
What happened?

09:42.440 --> 09:44.200
My mom said she'd come watch me play!

09:44.200 --> 09:45.670
-Really?
-Is it true?

09:45.670 --> 09:47.390
-Yes, for real!
-Then you must bring your A game!

09:47.390 --> 09:47.840
Sure thing!

09:47.840 --> 09:48.600
Are you done here?

09:48.600 --> 09:49.480
Boss has ordered

09:49.480 --> 09:50.840
the fist-shaped meatballs for us.
Come on.

09:50.840 --> 09:51.970
-Let's go eat!
-Let's go!

09:51.970 --> 09:53.920
How nice of Boss.

09:54.670 --> 09:56.480
Everything I covered in today's class
is key knowledge.

09:56.480 --> 09:59.010
Make sure you review it properly
afterwards.

10:05.150 --> 10:08.080
Why are the three of you standing
while taking notes?

10:09.670 --> 10:12.080
Miss, the words...

10:12.080 --> 10:13.120
seem clearer this way.

10:13.120 --> 10:13.600
Fine.

10:13.600 --> 10:14.910
Finish it, and you'll be dismissed.

10:14.910 --> 10:16.030
Okay, got it.

10:19.870 --> 10:21.110
Hey, the three of you!

10:44.840 --> 10:46.200
Let me take over. Let me!

10:46.870 --> 10:47.800
Defense needed!

10:49.600 --> 10:51.510
The coach told you
to shut down the opponent,

10:51.510 --> 10:53.170
not to miss the ball entirely.

10:54.440 --> 10:55.840
Just you wait.

10:56.270 --> 10:57.910
Is it just me or has Boss
become completely different?

10:57.910 --> 11:00.120
He doesn't argue with Wen Chengye anymore.

11:00.120 --> 11:02.360
He's afraid that Ms. Lin is too poor

11:02.360 --> 11:04.160
to afford a second lesson for us.

11:04.960 --> 11:05.360
Serve!

11:05.360 --> 11:05.790
Here!

11:33.630 --> 11:34.490
I'll take this.

11:34.720 --> 11:36.480
This scarf is priced at 308 yuan.

11:36.480 --> 11:37.360
Not a problem.

11:56.600 --> 11:58.150
Anything on my face?

11:59.240 --> 12:00.390
No.

12:01.320 --> 12:02.640
I just...

12:03.150 --> 12:04.280
wanted to thank you.

12:06.080 --> 12:06.720
For what?

12:07.480 --> 12:08.790
For changing

12:09.080 --> 12:11.360
your attitude toward those brats.

12:12.360 --> 12:13.360
Have you noticed

12:13.630 --> 12:16.090
that you've smiled at them
a lot more lately?

12:16.720 --> 12:17.630
Have I?

12:18.240 --> 12:19.500
Yes, you have.

12:19.600 --> 12:20.360
If you don't believe it,

12:20.360 --> 12:22.220
I'll take photos of you tomorrow.

12:22.840 --> 12:23.970
You're so childish.

12:28.080 --> 12:29.240
Although I don't know

12:29.240 --> 12:31.200
how long you'll stay here,

12:32.960 --> 12:35.510
I still need to thank you
for acknowledging them.

12:35.510 --> 12:36.470
It truly

12:36.600 --> 12:37.630
means a lot.

12:40.120 --> 12:41.400
But my recognition

12:41.750 --> 12:43.350
can't help them win the game.

12:43.440 --> 12:44.840
Don't worry about that.

12:44.840 --> 12:45.840
These days,

12:45.840 --> 12:47.750
they are clearly eager

12:47.750 --> 12:49.550
to ask for additional practice.

12:49.960 --> 12:52.220
If drive alone led to success every time,

12:52.550 --> 12:53.680
this world

12:53.870 --> 12:55.130
would be much simpler.

12:56.720 --> 12:59.390
At least
they're highly motivated now, right?

13:00.000 --> 13:00.960
Such passion is enough

13:00.960 --> 13:01.630
to help them

13:02.200 --> 13:02.800
win a game.

13:03.750 --> 13:05.350
But to keep a winning streak,

13:05.360 --> 13:06.560
it's far from enough.

13:07.360 --> 13:08.000
Were you

13:08.000 --> 13:10.390
just born this preachy?

13:11.630 --> 13:12.670
Ms. Lin,

13:13.000 --> 13:15.800
I'm talking about
the cruel reality of this world.

13:55.680 --> 13:58.120
[Three weeks later]

13:58.480 --> 14:00.480
That hoity-toity young master
wants to play cool.

14:00.480 --> 14:02.240
Just let him be.

14:03.890 --> 14:06.320
Still, I think we should
play it safe and focus on

14:06.320 --> 14:08.050
defense before striking back.

14:10.360 --> 14:11.360
Look at the time.

14:11.360 --> 14:12.600
Why isn't the coach here yet?

14:12.600 --> 14:14.800
We'll be late if he doesn't show up soon.

14:16.200 --> 14:17.240
You guys go without me.

14:17.240 --> 14:18.960
I'm running a bit late for something.

14:18.960 --> 14:20.000
The coach isn't around now,

14:20.000 --> 14:21.240
but we've done much practice

14:21.240 --> 14:22.320
-on Tactic No. 1.
-Ms Lin,

14:22.320 --> 14:24.120
you still can't reach the coach?

14:24.600 --> 14:26.960
He said he'd run a bit late for something.

14:29.630 --> 14:30.870
Let's set out now.

14:30.870 --> 14:31.630
Okay.

14:51.120 --> 14:53.320
We've arrived. Wake up, guys.

14:54.200 --> 14:55.240
Really, I mean...

15:03.200 --> 15:05.080
Coach Wang, where are you now?

15:09.910 --> 15:12.030
We've arrived at the court.

15:14.630 --> 15:17.030
Are you bailing on us
due to some emergency?

15:21.000 --> 15:22.660
This had better not get dirty.

15:23.750 --> 15:24.390
Fu,

15:24.390 --> 15:25.720
are you dating someone?

15:26.440 --> 15:27.480
Cut that nonsense.

15:27.480 --> 15:29.280
I bought this as a gift for my mom.

15:30.600 --> 15:32.400
You should have said so earlier.

15:34.630 --> 15:35.270
Well...

15:35.750 --> 15:36.550
Ms. Lin,

15:37.270 --> 15:39.470
is the coach still coming, at this hour?

15:41.900 --> 15:43.280
[Are you bailing on us
due to some emergency?]

15:44.630 --> 15:46.720
The coach is probably
held back by something.

15:46.720 --> 15:49.250
What could be more important
than this match?

15:50.790 --> 15:51.720
The clock is ticking.

15:51.720 --> 15:52.580
Let's go in now.

15:53.440 --> 15:54.640
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

16:14.000 --> 16:15.530
An iced Americano, please.

16:21.020 --> 16:21.380
[Coach Wang, where are you now?]

16:21.400 --> 16:21.770
[We've arrived at the court]

16:21.800 --> 16:22.630
[Are you bailing on us
due to some emergency?]

16:23.030 --> 16:24.080
Your Americano.

16:24.080 --> 16:24.840
Thanks.

16:35.840 --> 16:36.960
You must remember the tactics

16:36.960 --> 16:38.440
we talked about before the match.

16:38.440 --> 16:39.480
Exploit the rival team's weaknesses.

16:39.480 --> 16:40.750
Play it safe and steady.

16:40.750 --> 16:41.950
At last, win the game.

16:42.360 --> 16:43.200
Can you do it?

16:43.200 --> 16:44.130
-Yes!
-Yes!

16:44.160 --> 16:45.040
Can you nail it?

16:45.060 --> 16:45.900
-Yes!
-Yes!

16:50.840 --> 16:51.630
Lyujing!

16:52.200 --> 16:54.060
-We've got this!
-We've got this!

16:55.120 --> 16:56.980
-We've got this!
-We've got this!

16:58.360 --> 17:00.220
-We've got this!
-We've got this!

17:04.349 --> 17:05.109
Ms. Lin,

17:06.240 --> 17:07.349
is the coach still coming?

17:07.349 --> 17:08.440
Yeah, is he coming?

17:08.440 --> 17:09.510
Do you even need to ask?

17:09.510 --> 17:10.440
He has clearly bailed on us,

17:10.440 --> 17:12.640
as the situation has spoken for itself.

17:13.920 --> 17:15.260
The match hasn't begun yet.

17:15.260 --> 17:16.720
Let's be patient and wait.

17:24.960 --> 17:25.510
Hello?

17:25.960 --> 17:27.450
Something came up.
I can't make it to the site.

17:27.450 --> 17:28.700
Is it the coach?

17:29.550 --> 17:30.480
What's with him?

17:30.750 --> 17:31.680
Give me a second.

17:31.830 --> 17:32.830
What happened?

17:32.830 --> 17:34.090
How are you not coming?

17:34.440 --> 17:35.510
This is an important day.

17:35.510 --> 17:36.720
How could you stand us up?

17:36.720 --> 17:37.590
What about the players?

17:37.590 --> 17:38.790
What about the match?

17:39.400 --> 17:40.600
Put them on the phone.

17:41.640 --> 17:43.370
The coach wants a word with you.

17:43.830 --> 17:44.740
-Coach.
-Coach.

17:44.740 --> 17:45.660
-Are you coming?
-Coach.

17:45.660 --> 17:46.960
The match will begin in a bit.

17:46.960 --> 17:48.070
You're backing out or what?

17:48.070 --> 17:49.470
I'm not going to the site.

17:50.070 --> 17:50.640
I knew this would happen.

17:50.640 --> 17:51.070
Without you,

17:51.070 --> 17:52.440
how do we deal with this?

17:52.440 --> 17:53.070
We can't play in this case, Coach.

17:53.070 --> 17:54.600
So, are you chickening out?

17:59.480 --> 18:00.070
How is that possible?

18:00.070 --> 18:01.440
We'll definitely play this match.

18:01.440 --> 18:03.070
We'd sooner finish the game than quit.

18:03.070 --> 18:04.960
-Yeah. We'll crush Lyujing.
-We're going to defeat them.

18:04.960 --> 18:06.310
We'll surely play this match.

18:06.310 --> 18:07.060
Good.

18:07.440 --> 18:08.940
Then forget about me, and bear in mind

18:08.940 --> 18:10.940
what you have to do in the first half.

18:11.480 --> 18:13.510
That is to stick to Tactic No. 1,
defense before offense.

18:13.510 --> 18:15.590
Coach, when should we
assume the offensive?

18:15.590 --> 18:17.390
You'll know when the time comes.

18:17.590 --> 18:18.650
Remind yourselves

18:19.070 --> 18:20.870
of the first lesson I taught you.

18:21.880 --> 18:23.070
-Defense before offense.
-When to strike, Coach?

18:23.070 --> 18:23.960
What do you mean?

18:23.960 --> 18:24.960
-What?
-Coach?

18:25.920 --> 18:26.480
He just hung up.

18:26.480 --> 18:27.110
Hello?

18:28.000 --> 18:29.000
-Hello?
-No way.

18:29.350 --> 18:31.510
What does this mean:
"We'll know when the time comes"?

18:31.510 --> 18:34.000
Wasn't the first lesson about
playing defense before offense?

18:34.000 --> 18:34.920
Yeah.

18:34.920 --> 18:35.870
Alright, whatever.

18:35.870 --> 18:37.600
Let's just do as the coach said.

18:38.200 --> 18:39.750
Have some faith in the coach.

18:39.750 --> 18:40.350
Let's warm up.

18:40.350 --> 18:41.200
We don't have a coach again.

18:41.200 --> 18:43.860
Those with no coach
are always looked down upon.

18:43.880 --> 18:44.720
Come on, guys.

18:45.350 --> 18:46.590
Huddle now.

18:47.200 --> 18:48.000
Come on!

18:56.480 --> 18:57.410
Ms. Lin.

19:02.200 --> 19:03.550
Hongjing No. 8 High School!

19:03.550 --> 19:05.720
-We've got this!
-We've got this!

19:06.110 --> 19:06.780
-Alright.
-Let's go!

19:06.780 --> 19:07.270
Go!

19:10.480 --> 19:12.030
Today, Lyujing International School

19:12.030 --> 19:14.440
is playing Hongjing No. 8 High School.

19:14.440 --> 19:16.440
The former is known for
its lightning-fast attacks,

19:16.440 --> 19:18.680
while the latter secured a tie

19:18.680 --> 19:20.680
with surprising long balls

19:20.680 --> 19:22.200
and successful offside trap breaks

19:22.200 --> 19:23.680
in the previous match.

19:23.680 --> 19:24.880
An experienced team with great rhythm

19:24.880 --> 19:26.830
is here to play some new elites
with unpredictable tactics.

19:26.830 --> 19:30.110
A clash of speed and wisdom
is about to unfold.

19:32.510 --> 19:33.440
The game starts now.

19:33.440 --> 19:34.550
The kickoff is taken

19:34.550 --> 19:37.950
by Jiang Tianyu in white,
captain of Lyujing International.

19:39.000 --> 19:40.000
-You've got this!
-Here!

19:40.000 --> 19:42.680
-Go for it!
-You've got this!

19:42.680 --> 19:44.790
Keeping possession of the ball well,

19:44.790 --> 19:47.720
Lyujing International has launched
a quick attack.

19:53.350 --> 19:54.410
Defense! Defense!

19:55.030 --> 19:55.640
The left!

19:55.640 --> 19:56.440
Pass the ball!

19:59.030 --> 19:59.830
Lin Lu,

19:59.830 --> 20:01.830
didn't grow any taller lately, huh?

20:07.240 --> 20:08.310
Jiang Tianyu has the ball now.

20:08.310 --> 20:10.570
He's in the upper hand since he's taller.

20:13.440 --> 20:16.310
He chooses to pass the ball
to a midfield teammate.

20:17.240 --> 20:18.680
The players of Hongjing No. 8 High School

20:18.680 --> 20:20.880
are clearly setting up a solid defense.

20:23.440 --> 20:24.070
Liang!

20:24.070 --> 20:26.200
A chance for Hongjing No. 8 High School
to attack!

20:26.200 --> 20:27.200
Qin!

20:28.550 --> 20:29.200
Go!

20:29.200 --> 20:30.830
Such an intense situation.

20:30.830 --> 20:33.240
Lyujing International
has been trying to attack,

20:33.240 --> 20:36.590
yet they're always intercepted by Hongjing
at crucial moments.

20:36.590 --> 20:38.510
Compared to the previous match
against Ning'an,

20:38.510 --> 20:40.440
Hongjing No. 8 High School has made

20:40.440 --> 20:41.640
noticeable improvement

20:41.640 --> 20:43.640
in execution and cohesity.

20:43.640 --> 20:46.500
The core of Tactic No. 1 lies in
playing defense before offense.

20:46.500 --> 20:48.030
Our defensive strategy this time

20:48.030 --> 20:49.960
is to constrict
the rival team's attacking front,

20:49.960 --> 20:52.070
while seeking a chance
to assume the offensive.

20:52.070 --> 20:53.960
Defenders must watch the distance
between each other

20:53.960 --> 20:55.360
and spread out like a net.

20:55.790 --> 20:56.830
Keep watch!

20:58.080 --> 20:59.230
The back! The back!

21:10.960 --> 21:12.480
-Good shot!
-Fu!

21:14.350 --> 21:15.070
Bro,

21:15.070 --> 21:16.920
seems like your skills are poor as ever.

21:16.920 --> 21:18.510
On the field, Lin Lu

21:18.510 --> 21:19.750
and his former teammate Jiang Tianyu

21:19.750 --> 21:21.550
are communicating on amiable terms.

21:21.550 --> 21:23.240
-Here!
-Hongjing has put up an effective defense!

21:23.240 --> 21:25.030
Lyujing International
hasn't scored a goal yet.

21:25.030 --> 21:26.920
However, in the front, Hongjing only has

21:26.920 --> 21:29.400
Qin Ao, number 9, as the forward.

21:29.400 --> 21:30.750
Qin Ao is guarded by many

21:30.750 --> 21:32.470
and has no chance to score.

21:32.470 --> 21:33.960
Oh no, he lost the ball!

21:33.960 --> 21:36.070
Qin Ao just hit the ground hard.

21:36.070 --> 21:38.530
He staggered a bit
when getting up to defend.

21:39.070 --> 21:40.400
Believe in yourselves.

21:41.000 --> 21:42.030
You'll win this.

21:43.350 --> 21:44.400
One against many...

21:44.400 --> 21:45.660
This is too difficult.

21:46.310 --> 21:48.480
Lyujing is so overbearing.

21:49.200 --> 21:50.530
They're way out of line.

21:57.480 --> 21:58.590
Why does he have to act cool?

21:58.590 --> 21:59.310
The first half of the game

21:59.310 --> 22:00.350
-is coming to an end.
-Let me!

22:00.350 --> 22:02.750
Lyujing International
launched multiple attacks.

22:02.750 --> 22:04.750
All Hongjing players just retreated
for defense.

22:04.750 --> 22:05.830
They're waiting for a chance.

22:05.830 --> 22:07.830
Seems like Hongjing
has adopted the strategy

22:07.830 --> 22:09.350
of playing defense before offense today.

22:09.350 --> 22:09.790
That said,

22:09.790 --> 22:13.200
the essence of this strategy is launching
one decisive attack to secure victory.

22:13.200 --> 22:16.230
Let's see how they find the right moment.

22:17.070 --> 22:18.510
Still a coward, huh?

22:18.510 --> 22:20.830
You had no gut to attack
though you had the ball.

22:20.830 --> 22:21.890
You're like trash.

22:26.240 --> 22:28.040
Soon you won't be this arrogant.

22:28.680 --> 22:29.680
You didn't show up

22:29.680 --> 22:30.880
or even leave an instruction.

22:30.880 --> 22:31.920
How's that appropriate?

22:31.920 --> 22:33.650
Don't forget you are the coach.

22:36.550 --> 22:37.750
The first half is over.

22:37.750 --> 22:39.830
Zero to Zero, a tie for the time being.

22:39.830 --> 22:40.760
Have some water.

22:47.270 --> 22:48.550
What did the coach say?

22:50.000 --> 22:51.260
He hasn't replied yet.

22:51.510 --> 22:53.750
Anyway, just keep your composure.

22:53.750 --> 22:54.750
You played the first half well.

22:54.750 --> 22:55.440
"Well"?

22:55.440 --> 22:56.940
It went terrible.

22:57.270 --> 22:58.550
We didn't even launch a decent attack.

22:58.550 --> 22:59.830
It's true that we defended
all the attacks,

22:59.830 --> 23:01.480
but the pressure
on the backcourt players was too heavy.

23:01.480 --> 23:02.310
We couldn't keep up physically,

23:02.310 --> 23:04.550
since we were on the back foot
the entire time.

23:04.550 --> 23:06.590
I alone simply can't
break through a group of people.

23:06.590 --> 23:07.550
What is it called?

23:07.550 --> 23:09.400
"One cannot tango."

23:09.550 --> 23:10.340
Boss,

23:10.550 --> 23:11.680
the correct saying is
"it takes two to tango."

23:11.680 --> 23:12.880
You know what I mean.

23:13.750 --> 23:14.680
Pool your strength together.

23:14.680 --> 23:16.830
I believe you can win this.
Just go for it.

23:16.830 --> 23:17.550
Yeah.

23:18.200 --> 23:19.640
Qin Ao is the only forward anyway.

23:19.640 --> 23:21.030
All the strength is there already.

23:21.030 --> 23:22.310
No matter what, backcourt players

23:22.310 --> 23:23.640
just focus on passing the ball.

23:23.640 --> 23:25.310
Catch every window
to pass it to the front court.

23:25.310 --> 23:26.920
Is passing the ball to you of any help?

23:26.920 --> 23:28.000
Idiot.

23:28.000 --> 23:30.330
Better than passing it to you, right, bro?

23:31.310 --> 23:33.400
Let's put in more effort
in the second half.

23:33.400 --> 23:34.160
We'll try our best, guys!

23:34.160 --> 23:35.000
-Seek a chance to strike back.
-We've got this!

23:35.000 --> 23:36.860
-We've got this!
-We've got this.

23:44.240 --> 23:45.770
An iced Americano, thanks.

23:52.670 --> 23:54.930
Did you come here for a business meeting?

23:56.510 --> 23:59.240
A bid conference will commence here
in half an hour.

23:59.240 --> 24:00.480
I heard you were around,

24:00.480 --> 24:01.410
so I came see you.

24:02.200 --> 24:03.400
Just the same as ever.

24:03.750 --> 24:06.270
Someone's using me
to gain favors with others again.

24:06.270 --> 24:08.350
Having value means being needed.

24:08.350 --> 24:09.350
It's a good thing.

24:12.880 --> 24:14.940
There is a word carved on my forehead–

24:16.880 --> 24:17.750
"priceless."

24:21.030 --> 24:22.680
Now I finally see

24:22.680 --> 24:24.960
Dad's genes at play in you.

24:29.030 --> 24:31.160
Your players are having a fierce game,

24:31.480 --> 24:33.550
while you are sitting here
drinking coffee.

24:33.550 --> 24:36.400
Seems like they don't hold much value
in your heart.

24:36.400 --> 24:37.800
You're overthinking it.

24:38.310 --> 24:41.040
I simply think
that as Hongjing's interim coach,

24:41.680 --> 24:42.400
there's no need to create

24:42.400 --> 24:44.830
the false impression
that I'll stay for the long haul,

24:44.830 --> 24:46.960
and hence upset them when we part ways.

24:48.270 --> 24:50.200
Besides, Lyujing isn't that good.

24:51.030 --> 24:52.490
Hongjing can handle them.

24:55.240 --> 24:56.170
My dear brother,

24:56.960 --> 24:58.560
you love this football team.

25:00.110 --> 25:01.790
No, I'm just testing my abilities.

25:01.790 --> 25:02.890
That's an excuse.

25:03.110 --> 25:04.840
Don't you think I know you well?

25:05.480 --> 25:07.960
You've grown fond
of this two-bit football team over time.

25:07.960 --> 25:09.310
I'm just curious.

25:09.310 --> 25:10.640
Why would you pick it?

25:11.270 --> 25:12.920
You never act on impulse.

25:13.310 --> 25:14.590
The point is,

25:14.590 --> 25:16.000
this team is really bad.

25:16.000 --> 25:17.720
It shouldn't have caught your eye.

25:17.720 --> 25:18.310
So?

25:18.310 --> 25:20.640
So, this team is not your target.

25:22.240 --> 25:23.560
I've asked Yu Bo.

25:23.680 --> 25:24.680
He wouldn't tell.

25:25.310 --> 25:27.040
But I already have a rough idea.

25:31.240 --> 25:33.100
The second half is about to begin.

25:33.160 --> 25:35.020
I don't have time to chat with you.

25:40.200 --> 25:41.480
I hope you know what you're doing

25:41.480 --> 25:42.750
and never waste your ability

25:42.750 --> 25:44.030
on pointless causes.

25:47.550 --> 25:48.400
Ji,

25:49.000 --> 25:49.960
I'm done here.

25:49.960 --> 25:51.160
Bring the car around.

25:59.890 --> 26:03.120
[The second half]

26:00.240 --> 26:02.270
The second half begins.

26:05.200 --> 26:06.240
Run! Run!

26:06.240 --> 26:08.160
Put up a defense!

26:08.160 --> 26:11.220
Lyujing players are encouraging
each other to attack.

26:11.310 --> 26:12.000
Yes, pass it along!

26:12.000 --> 26:14.000
-Pass the ball along!
-Pass the ball!

26:14.000 --> 26:16.230
We can tell that Lyujing International's
attacks in the second half

26:16.230 --> 26:16.960
are much fiercer.

26:16.960 --> 26:18.830
-Run faster!
-But this will expose

26:18.830 --> 26:20.440
an obvious loophole in their defense.

26:20.440 --> 26:21.720
For Hongjing No. 8 High School,

26:21.720 --> 26:23.070
it's a good opportunity to counterattack,

26:23.070 --> 26:24.030
provided

26:24.030 --> 26:26.270
that they withstand such an onslaught.

26:26.270 --> 26:26.830
Good shot!

26:26.830 --> 26:27.510
Bravo!

26:37.350 --> 26:38.610
Time for a corner kick.

26:38.790 --> 26:40.190
Come on, put up a defense!

26:41.270 --> 26:42.600
They're playing at too fast a pace.

26:42.600 --> 26:44.030
Just a stamina test, isn't it?

26:44.030 --> 26:44.830
I can match up.

26:46.400 --> 26:47.550
Don't get carried away.

26:47.550 --> 26:49.750
Remind yourself of what the coach said.

26:50.720 --> 26:52.360
Lyujing is best at rhythm,

26:52.380 --> 26:53.300
not stamina.

26:53.330 --> 26:54.500
You must stall and exhaust

26:54.500 --> 26:55.320
them.

26:56.920 --> 26:58.310
"Exhaust them."

26:58.550 --> 27:00.480
But it'll kill me not to strike now.

27:00.510 --> 27:02.070
Just try to hold steady.

27:04.350 --> 27:06.440
Lyujing International just won
a corner kick in the front court.

27:06.440 --> 27:08.110
It will be taken by Player No. 4.

27:08.110 --> 27:09.640
Get the defense set up well!

27:11.750 --> 27:14.080
Let's see his choice for this corner kick.

27:14.720 --> 27:16.440
The ball went for the goal

27:17.880 --> 27:20.790
and was pushed away
by Hongjing's goalkeeper with one hand,

27:20.790 --> 27:23.050
which earned the team a chance to attack.

27:26.510 --> 27:29.240
They chose to bring the ball
to the left flank.

27:36.070 --> 27:38.720
Both teams are fighting fiercely
for the ball now.

27:38.720 --> 27:39.720
-The ball!
-Pass!

27:40.440 --> 27:41.510
-Lin Lu!
-Lin Lu!

27:41.510 --> 27:42.570
-Lin Lu!
-Go check on him!

27:42.570 --> 27:44.200
-A player got hurt and fell on defense.
-Lin Lu!

27:44.200 --> 27:45.330
Lin Lu, are you okay?

27:45.350 --> 27:46.350
-Lin Lu!
-Are you having a cramp?

27:46.350 --> 27:46.720
Lu,

27:46.720 --> 27:48.070
-are you okay?
-What happened?

27:48.070 --> 27:49.030
Don't move. Lie still.

27:49.030 --> 27:50.400
-Can you move your leg? Must be a cramp.
-Take a deep breath.

27:50.400 --> 27:51.270
Listen, raise your leg.

27:51.270 --> 27:52.590
-Don't fret, guys.
-How is Lin Lu?

27:52.590 --> 27:53.480
-I'll give you a spray and then a massage.
-Lin Lu!

27:53.480 --> 27:54.310
-Don't move. Don't move.
-Just position your leg right.

27:54.310 --> 27:55.310
Don't move.

28:04.860 --> 28:06.350
Later on, target Player No. 6.

28:06.350 --> 28:07.950
He can't hold on much longer.

28:09.240 --> 28:10.310
Come here, guys!

28:11.550 --> 28:12.880
No pressure, fellows.

28:14.720 --> 28:15.720
Come huddle!

28:16.440 --> 28:17.720
-Relax. Nice and slow.
-This is it.

28:17.720 --> 28:18.400
Relax. Just relax.

28:18.400 --> 28:21.460
They're definitely going to overload
on Lin Lu's side.

28:22.440 --> 28:23.840
I'll try to cover for him.

28:24.930 --> 28:25.990
But in this case...

28:25.990 --> 28:27.850
will we stand a chance of scoring?

28:33.440 --> 28:35.270
Forget about the 4-5-1 Formation.

28:35.270 --> 28:37.130
We might as well all play defense.

28:41.270 --> 28:41.880
"Well"?

28:41.880 --> 28:43.310
It went terrible.

28:43.310 --> 28:45.110
We didn't even launch a decent attack.

28:45.110 --> 28:46.000
What is it called?

28:46.000 --> 28:47.750
"One cannot tango."

28:48.400 --> 28:50.440
Boss, the correct saying is
"it takes two to tango."

28:50.440 --> 28:51.200
Pool your strength together.

28:51.200 --> 28:53.440
I believe you can win this.
Just go for it.

28:53.440 --> 28:54.640
Qin Ao is the only forward anyway.

28:54.640 --> 28:56.570
All the strength is there already.

28:58.000 --> 29:00.000
Coach, when should we
assume the offensive?

29:00.000 --> 29:01.860
You will know when the time comes.

29:02.160 --> 29:03.220
Remind yourselves

29:03.440 --> 29:05.240
of the first lesson I taught you.

29:07.440 --> 29:09.440
Blind obedience makes people numb.

29:10.070 --> 29:10.960
On the field,

29:11.550 --> 29:13.000
if players only follow orders

29:13.000 --> 29:14.310
without using their brains,

29:14.310 --> 29:15.480
that's a crime.

29:17.680 --> 29:19.920
The first lesson Coach taught us was not
playing defense before offense,

29:19.920 --> 29:21.400
nor the 4-5-1 Formation.

29:21.400 --> 29:22.680
It was that we must use our brains

29:22.680 --> 29:23.940
when we play football.

29:28.160 --> 29:29.480
Then what should we do?

29:30.400 --> 29:32.270
We need another forward besides you.

29:32.270 --> 29:33.270
Let's make it two.

29:37.640 --> 29:38.770
I'll take that role.

29:42.270 --> 29:43.270
That's more like it.

29:43.270 --> 29:44.870
Two on two. That's only fair.

29:51.760 --> 29:54.240
Today, I let you boys
take full charge of the match

29:54.240 --> 29:55.440
because I believe

29:55.440 --> 29:56.960
that even if I'm not on the site,

29:56.960 --> 29:58.920
you can still stay clear-headed

29:58.920 --> 30:00.000
and use your brains

30:00.000 --> 30:01.310
to win the game.

30:01.310 --> 30:04.400
You've got this!

30:04.400 --> 30:06.440
-Go for it!
-Well done!

30:06.440 --> 30:07.270
The formation's different now.

30:07.270 --> 30:08.850
Defense! Defense! Quick!

30:09.440 --> 30:10.610
Good job.

30:10.790 --> 30:13.310
-Defense!
-The primary issue isn't the formation,

30:13.310 --> 30:14.970
-but thinking.
-Pass it over!

30:16.230 --> 30:17.630
Cut through them!

30:18.160 --> 30:19.560
Steady the defense line!

30:25.160 --> 30:26.270
Congratulations, boys.

30:26.270 --> 30:28.440
You've finally seen the whole picture.

30:28.440 --> 30:29.720
The 4-4-2 Formation

30:29.720 --> 30:32.180
is the correct approach
for the second half.

30:33.590 --> 30:35.310
In the second half, Hongjing seems to have

30:35.310 --> 30:36.750
adopted a different approach

30:36.750 --> 30:38.830
and changed from the 4-5-1 Formation
to the 4-4-2 Formation.

30:38.830 --> 30:39.750
Such an alteration

30:39.750 --> 30:41.920
has opened some opportunities
or them to attack.

30:41.920 --> 30:43.680
-Get a move on. Put up a defense!
-No more dawdling.

30:43.680 --> 30:45.440
-P-Put up a defense!
-Defense!

30:48.880 --> 30:49.920
No need to rush.

30:50.010 --> 30:51.870
You will eventually score a goal.

30:52.550 --> 30:54.310
Come back here! Come!

30:55.160 --> 30:55.960
Coach.

30:55.960 --> 30:57.240
They've changed to the 4-4-2 Formation.

30:57.240 --> 30:58.110
Watch our defense line.

30:58.110 --> 30:59.480
Pick up the pace on offense.

30:59.480 --> 31:00.480
Got it, Coach.

31:01.550 --> 31:04.000
Have both forwards
suppress their center-backs,

31:04.000 --> 31:06.880
and never let Lyujing
easily break through the defense.

31:06.880 --> 31:07.920
What you need to do

31:07.940 --> 31:09.500
is push Lyujing further

31:09.890 --> 31:12.020
till weak spots show in their defense.

31:15.640 --> 31:18.790
Hongjing, Hongjing!

31:18.810 --> 31:21.790
Hongjing, Hongjing!

31:21.790 --> 31:23.650
When you take control of the pace,

31:24.480 --> 31:25.920
Lyujing's attacks will start to appear

31:25.920 --> 31:27.450
impatient and repetitive.

31:27.680 --> 31:29.830
Their formation
will be gradually compressed

31:29.830 --> 31:31.550
and turn like a stretched rubber band

31:31.550 --> 31:32.310
that could break anytime.

31:32.310 --> 31:33.310
Hold the line!

31:33.310 --> 31:34.310
Faster!

31:37.090 --> 31:38.510
Nice shot!

31:40.110 --> 31:41.710
-Go for it!
-You've got this!

31:47.070 --> 31:48.350
That was a pity.

31:53.550 --> 31:54.310
Fu!

31:54.880 --> 31:56.550
Jiang Tianyu, captain of Lyujing,

31:56.550 --> 31:58.880
knocked down Fu Xinshu,
captain of Hongjing!

31:58.880 --> 32:01.720
-Let's see what the referee calls.
-Fu!

32:09.790 --> 32:11.510
Are you okay, Fu?

32:11.510 --> 32:12.550
Fu!

32:13.030 --> 32:13.550
Are you okay?

32:13.550 --> 32:14.200
-Fu.
-Mind your movements.

32:14.200 --> 32:15.850
-Are you alright, Fu?
-I’m fine.

32:15.850 --> 32:17.480
Jiang, did you do that on purpose,
didn't you?

32:17.480 --> 32:19.030
Fight me, I dare you!

32:19.030 --> 32:20.160
What does this mean?

32:20.350 --> 32:20.880
Back to the game.

32:20.880 --> 32:21.830
Up for a fight, aren't you?

32:21.830 --> 32:23.070
Don't get physical!

32:26.680 --> 32:28.080
Just don't start a fight.

32:28.640 --> 32:29.350
Fu,

32:29.350 --> 32:31.610
-how are you holding up?
-I'm doing okay.

32:32.070 --> 32:32.790
This is infuriating.

32:32.790 --> 32:33.650
All's fine now.

32:34.270 --> 32:35.000
All's fine.

32:43.720 --> 32:45.400
The referee gave Jiang Tianyu, captain

32:45.400 --> 32:47.790
of Lyujing International,
a yellow card as a warning.

32:47.790 --> 32:48.680
Hongjing No. 8 High School

32:48.680 --> 32:50.270
has been awarded a set piece,

32:50.270 --> 32:52.310
which will be taken by Fu Xinshu.

32:52.310 --> 32:53.750
But given that their both forwards

32:53.750 --> 32:56.000
are being heavily guarded
by Lyujing International,

32:56.000 --> 32:58.240
Hongjing's best passing lane
has been cut off.

32:58.240 --> 32:59.000
Right now,

32:59.000 --> 33:00.240
all the pressure

33:00.240 --> 33:01.070
is on Fu Xinshu.

33:01.070 --> 33:04.240
-Here!
-Will he find that one only crack?

33:12.960 --> 33:13.720
Coach!

33:14.310 --> 33:16.160
May I ask you a question?

33:16.720 --> 33:17.480
Well,

33:17.910 --> 33:20.370
what's the most important job
for a captain?

33:22.550 --> 33:24.210
It is to trust your teammates.

33:24.790 --> 33:26.480
I-Is it that simple?

33:29.750 --> 33:31.610
It is your teammates' trust in you

33:31.920 --> 33:33.580
that makes you their captain.

33:34.120 --> 33:35.400
At critical moments,

33:35.420 --> 33:36.240
trusting your teammates

33:36.240 --> 33:38.100
matters more than anything else.

33:38.640 --> 33:39.700
A captain has to see

33:40.000 --> 33:41.860
the potential in every teammate.

33:56.000 --> 33:57.110
Wen Chengye!

33:58.480 --> 34:01.440
Fu Xinshu passed the ball
to Player No. 11, Wen Chengye.

34:01.440 --> 34:03.720
The latter caught the ball with his chest.

34:03.720 --> 34:04.550
Destroy their defense!

34:04.550 --> 34:07.070
Jiang Tianyu tried to turn the tables
with a slide tackle.

34:07.070 --> 34:08.000
But Wen Chengye

34:08.000 --> 34:09.150
pulled the ball back

34:09.150 --> 34:11.280
and easily moved it around Jiang Tianyu.

34:09.350 --> 34:12.949
[Hongjing No. 8 High School Football Team]

34:13.920 --> 34:16.320
Wen Chengye passed the ball
to Player No. 7, Chen Jianghe.

34:16.320 --> 34:18.719
The ball paused
and went right for the goal.

34:19.510 --> 34:21.960
Player No. 9 Qin Ao headed the ball.

34:21.960 --> 34:22.920
Goal!

34:22.920 --> 34:24.190
A superb piece of teamwork!

34:24.190 --> 34:25.320
One to zero!

34:25.320 --> 34:27.030
When you have faith in yourselves,

34:27.030 --> 34:28.150
you will win.

34:27.860 --> 34:31.150
♪ No matter how long the road ahead ♪

34:30.670 --> 34:32.710
Time's up. The game is over.

34:32.070 --> 34:34.330
♪ Nothing can stop me ♪

34:32.710 --> 34:34.000
Congratulations
to Hongjing No. 8 High School

34:34.000 --> 34:36.400
for winning the game
with a score of one to zero,

34:35.830 --> 34:37.489
♪ Break through every haze of doubt ♪

34:36.400 --> 34:39.840
remaining undefeated
in the first two matches.

34:38.100 --> 34:39.929
♪ Chase the light within me ♪

34:40.550 --> 34:43.210
♪ Strong wings grow through the storm ♪

34:43.860 --> 34:47.040
♪ Even if no one cheers ♪

34:47.780 --> 34:50.219
♪ I'll keep fighting my way through ♪

34:51.830 --> 34:53.760
♪ On a deserted battlefield ♪

34:54.310 --> 34:55.889
♪ I grow stronger
with a resounding voice ♪

34:56.300 --> 34:59.690
♪ I'll take every scar ♪

35:00.060 --> 35:03.990
♪ As my badge of honor ♪

35:16.770 --> 35:19.480
♪ If facing every storm is ♪

35:20.360 --> 35:23.440
♪ What it takes to grow ♪

35:24.320 --> 35:26.360
Coach, I can't believe
you hid somewhere intentionally.

35:24.450 --> 35:27.060
♪ I will stubbornly
go against the current ♪

35:24.620 --> 35:31.090
[South Grandstand Entrance 1]

35:26.360 --> 35:27.760
That was way out of line.

35:27.760 --> 35:28.710
What do you think?

35:27.990 --> 35:30.720
♪ And let myself go wild ♪

35:28.710 --> 35:30.110
A nice kick, wasn't it?

35:30.110 --> 35:31.230
Coach, I'm telling you,

35:31.230 --> 35:32.670
that winning goal was amazing.

35:32.670 --> 35:33.630
-What did you have to do with it?
-No, Boss...

35:33.630 --> 35:35.230
I put up a great defense with a kick.

35:35.230 --> 35:36.280
Listen, listen.

35:36.060 --> 35:37.170
[Mom]

35:36.280 --> 35:37.710
This was a real eye-opener.

35:37.170 --> 35:38.830
[Call History]

35:37.710 --> 35:39.320
You've got a lot to learn.

35:39.320 --> 35:42.480
-Bro...
-I completely nailed the game.

35:42.480 --> 35:43.880
He's lost all his dignity
after that stupid transfer.

35:43.300 --> 35:44.760
[South Grandstand Entrance 1]

35:43.880 --> 35:45.480
The transfer left him no choice but...

35:45.480 --> 35:47.230
Here comes the bus.

35:49.640 --> 35:50.310
-Let's go.
-Fu Xinshu,

35:50.310 --> 35:51.070
-anything wrong?
-Let's go.

35:51.070 --> 35:52.030
Ms. Lin,

35:52.280 --> 35:53.880
my mom promised to come watch my game,

35:53.880 --> 35:55.140
but she didn't show up.

35:56.070 --> 35:57.070
Have you reached her yet?

35:57.070 --> 35:59.800
I called her many times
but couldn't get through.

35:59.800 --> 36:01.440
She mentioned before that she felt unwell

36:01.440 --> 36:02.570
and needed surgery.

36:04.960 --> 36:07.090
Could something have happened to her?

36:07.840 --> 36:08.790
Don't fret.

36:09.150 --> 36:10.000
Ms. Lin,

36:10.000 --> 36:12.130
has something really happened to her?

36:14.110 --> 36:15.360
Calm down. Calm down.

36:16.070 --> 36:17.930
How about I go with you to find her?

36:18.320 --> 36:19.740
I don't know where she is.

36:20.510 --> 36:21.590
Let's head to your home first.

36:21.590 --> 36:22.360
If things get tough...

36:22.360 --> 36:24.070
Then I'll figure out a solution.

36:24.070 --> 36:25.000
I'll go with you.

36:26.150 --> 36:27.550
W-We will go with you too.

36:27.760 --> 36:28.410
No.

36:28.630 --> 36:29.830
Too many cooks spoil the broth.

36:29.830 --> 36:30.880
You guys wait at the hotel.

36:30.880 --> 36:33.280
I'll keep you updated
if anything comes up.

36:33.440 --> 36:34.640
Okay. Off you go then.

36:35.110 --> 36:35.880
Don't worry.

36:35.880 --> 36:37.150
I'll call a cab
and take you to find her now.

36:37.150 --> 36:37.680
Let's go.

36:43.630 --> 36:45.550
Hey, are you leaving with them or...

36:45.550 --> 36:47.630
Sir, no need to wait for him.

36:48.760 --> 36:51.400
The young lord here only rides
in his designated car.

36:51.400 --> 36:52.150
Let's go!

37:00.880 --> 37:01.630
Drive, sir.

37:02.290 --> 37:03.190
We can set out now.

37:03.190 --> 37:04.450
You can drive now, sir.

37:06.110 --> 37:07.710
Sir, I'll scan the Wechat payment code.
How much?

37:07.710 --> 37:09.030
I have cash on me.

37:09.030 --> 37:10.030
You have cash?

37:14.010 --> 37:21.570
[The Royal Court]

37:15.490 --> 37:17.420
What are you doing? Come back here!

37:18.230 --> 37:19.150
Fu Xinshu!

37:19.590 --> 37:21.110
-Fu Xinshu!
-Hold on!

37:21.670 --> 37:23.230
Even in a rush, you must register first.

37:23.230 --> 37:24.280
Your IDs, please.

37:31.400 --> 37:32.400
Get upstairs now.

37:35.190 --> 37:37.000
This violin cost a large sum of money.

37:37.000 --> 37:37.960
You must study hard.

37:37.960 --> 37:39.710
-Got it.
-Good boy.

37:47.710 --> 37:48.670
Mom,

37:48.670 --> 37:49.870
who is he?

37:50.070 --> 37:51.190
Get in here already.

37:51.190 --> 37:53.150
Why the dawdling? Who are you talking to?

37:53.150 --> 37:56.350
Someone's asking for directions.
I'll be right with you!

38:09.710 --> 38:10.590
Mom.

38:12.230 --> 38:13.440
Why did you come here?

38:14.000 --> 38:15.760
I couldn't reach you. I...

38:15.760 --> 38:16.800
You said you'd have surgery,

38:16.800 --> 38:18.330
but you didn't tell me when.

38:18.880 --> 38:21.340
I thought something happened to you,
so I...

38:22.920 --> 38:24.070
The hospital misdiagnosed.

38:24.070 --> 38:25.130
I'm actually well.

38:27.280 --> 38:29.210
A-And the money for the surgery...

38:30.950 --> 38:31.910
I've spent it.

38:32.190 --> 38:33.860
Your younger brother
plays the violin well.

38:33.860 --> 38:35.790
Uncle Li had to get him a better one.

38:35.840 --> 38:38.370
Alright. If there's nothing else,
off you go.

38:39.550 --> 38:41.230
Why did you lie to me?

38:45.880 --> 38:47.270
Every time

38:47.550 --> 38:49.280
you said you'd come see me,

38:50.480 --> 38:52.540
it was just to get me to wire you money.

38:55.840 --> 38:57.590
Why did you lie to me like that?

38:57.590 --> 38:59.000
I didn't lie to you.

38:59.000 --> 39:00.550
I really don't have time today.

39:00.550 --> 39:03.010
Besides, Uncle Li wouldn't let me
go see you.

39:05.550 --> 39:06.320
Mom,

39:07.590 --> 39:09.790
when will you ever have time to visit me?

39:09.880 --> 39:11.150
Enough, Xinshu.

39:11.150 --> 39:12.590
You're almost an adult.

39:12.590 --> 39:14.090
Stop being so harsh on me, okay?

39:14.090 --> 39:16.150
What do you mean by being harsh on you?

39:16.230 --> 39:18.030
Mom, have I done anything wrong?

39:19.590 --> 39:21.190
You said you needed surgery.

39:23.440 --> 39:26.440
So I gave you the entire sum of the money
Grandpa left me

39:27.400 --> 39:28.670
when he passed away, Mom.

39:28.670 --> 39:30.550
That was all I had.

39:32.070 --> 39:33.190
But you...

39:33.190 --> 39:35.440
you spent it on a violin for that boy.

39:36.630 --> 39:37.880
Then what about me?

39:38.760 --> 39:40.150
I did mess up on that issue.

39:40.150 --> 39:41.020
Xinshu,

39:41.360 --> 39:43.310
can you try to understand me?

39:43.440 --> 39:45.280
These years haven't been easy for me.

39:45.280 --> 39:47.280
It's not that I don't want to see you.

39:48.840 --> 39:50.370
But whenever I speak of you,

39:50.630 --> 39:52.200
Uncle Li gets mad,

39:52.440 --> 39:53.710
accusing me of neglecting the family

39:53.710 --> 39:55.440
and threatening to divorce me.

39:55.920 --> 39:57.310
I have no option.

39:57.360 --> 39:58.570
I admit I've done you wrong.

39:58.570 --> 40:00.380
Don't come find me again.

40:22.800 --> 40:24.280
-Fu Xinshu!
-Fu Xinshu!

40:25.550 --> 40:26.280
Are you okay?

40:26.590 --> 40:27.520
Are you alright?

40:28.360 --> 40:29.960
-Sorry about that.
-Thanks.

40:43.710 --> 40:45.000
I admit I've done you wrong.

40:45.000 --> 40:46.880
Don't come find me again.

41:48.590 --> 41:49.910
♪ There's nothing to fear ♪

41:51.000 --> 41:52.490
♪ Because you're with me ♪

41:55.250 --> 41:56.690
♪ The light shimmers ♪

41:57.930 --> 41:59.250
♪ Brilliant as stars ♪
